skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: huntsville on tap
des: Find out what's on tap in real-time at your favorite breweries in Huntsville, AL! The skill will provide you with three options: which breweries are in the area, what's on tap at your selected brewery, and what's new/popular. If you know which brewery you want to ask about, simply include it when you ask Alexa e.g. "Alexa, ask Huntsville On Tap what's at Straight to Ale".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
